semesterprojekt2017.client.rpc

Interface RPCServiceAsync


  • public interface RPCServiceAsync
    Used for calling the server to retrieve information and the server also uses this class (by the asyncCallback object) to call the client back once it has an answer to the request. All methods in this class are void, since the client shouldn't expect an answer instantly
